Government Medical College, Alwar is a medical school affiliated with Rajasthan University of Health Sciences situated in Alwar, Rajasthan. Alwar has two medical schools, the other being ESIC Medical College, Alwar. The college started taking MBBS students from 2023. The attached hospitals are Rajiv Gandhi General Hospital, Janana Hospital, Children's Hospital.
